  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Nutrition Education Project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project goal is to improve the nutritional status of people affected by leprosy and their family members in Bogra District. The objectives are to: a) increase awareness on nutritious food &amp; balanced diet among self-help group members and their families, b) improve beneficiaries understanding of the importance of vitamins &amp; minerals in our daily diet, and c) capacity building of the sub-district (upazila) federations</narrative>
  </description>
